'''鱂屬'''（'''''Cyprinodon'''''）是[[鯉齒鱂科|鯉齒鱂科]]下的一個[[屬|屬]]。其下生物主要發現於[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[加勒比地區|加勒比地區]]和[[美國南部|美國南部]]各地。其下有的[[種|種]]分佈並不集中，有些是[[特有種|特有種]]。<ref>Contreras Balderas, S., and W. Bussing (2013). ''[http://www.feow.org/ecoregions/details/175 Yucatan] {{Wayback|url=http://www.feow.org/ecoregions/details/175 |date=20181007223233 }}''. Freshwater Ecoregions of the World. Retrieved 1 March 2013.</ref><ref>Martin, C. H., and P. C. Wainwright (2013). ''Multiple Fitness Peaks on the Adaptive Landscape Drive Adaptive Radiation in the Wild.'' Science 339(6116): 208-211.</ref>

其下許多種的生存環境都受到了威脅，有的已經瀕臨滅絕。<ref>{{IUCN|id=6177 |title=''Cyprinodon ceciliae'' |assessors=Contreras-Balderas, S. & Almada-Villela, P. |version=2012.2 |year=1996 |accessdate=1 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{IUCN|id=6176 |title=''Cyprinodon inmemoriam'' |assessors=Contreras-Balderas, S. & Almada-Villela, P. |version=2012.2 |year=1996 |accessdate=1 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{IUCN|id=6155 |title=''Cyprinodon latifasciatus'' |assessors=Contreras-Balderas, S. & Almada-Villela, P. |version=2012.2 |year=1996 |accessdate=1 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{IUCN|id=6168 |title=''Cyprinodon spp.'' |assessors=Contreras-Balderas, S. & Almada-Villela, P. |version=2012.2 |year=1996 |accessdate=1 March 2013}}</ref> ''C. alvarezi'' 和 ''C. longidorsalis'' 已經在野外滅絕。<ref>{{IUCN|id=6144 |title=''Cyprinodon alvarezi'' |assessors=Contreras-Balderas, S. & Almada-Villela, P. |version=2012.2 |year=1996 |accessdate=1 March 2013}}</ref><ref>{{IUCN|id=6174 |title=''Cyprinodon longidorsalis'' |assessors=Contreras-Balderas, S. & Almada-Villela, P. |version=2012.2 |year=1996 |accessdate=1 March 2013}}</ref>

鱂屬生物個體都較小，最大的不{{convert|10|cm}}，平均長度只有此數據的一半。<ref name=FishBase>{{FishBase genus | genus = Cyprinodon| month = August | year = 2013}}</ref>

